headline: Teradyne (TER) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of semiconductor testing company Teradyne (NASDAQ:TER) jumped 3.2% in the morning session after the company announced the launch of its new ETS-800 D20 system, a platform designed for testing power semiconductors.

headline: Earnings Preview: What to Expect From Teradyne’s Report

headline: Teradyne Announces the ETS-800 Dual Sector Automated Test System
summary: NORTH READING, Mass, October 06, 2025--Teradyne is proud to announce the ETS-800 D20, the latest addition to the ETS-800 platform of high-performance test systems for power semiconductors.
